(18, 'Dương Minh Đức', 'duc@gmail.com', 'Hà Nội', 'Hello everyone! Today I will introduce myself. My name is Ha. I was born and grow up in Hai Phong. I’m 18 years old. There are four members in my family: my father, my mother, my younger brother and me. My father is a driver taxi. He is 42 years old. He has to leave home very early and comes home very late. He works hard to earn for a living. My mother is a farmer. She is 39 years old. Everyday, she works on farm. She plants many kinds of food such as rice and lots of vegetables. She also raises animals such as chickens, pigs, ducks,… She’s very hard-working. Both my father and mother work hard to earn money in order to bring us up. I love my parents very much. My younger brother, Tuan, is a student. ', '1', '1554435326avatar1.png', 3, 0),
(19, 'Phạm Văn Tuấn ', 'tuan@gmail.com', 'Lưu Kiếm, Thủy Nguyên, Hải Phòng', NULL, '1', '1554436849avatar2.png', 2, 0);

